<div class ="about">
<h3> About Syracuse Uprise </h3>
<p> We are a non-profit organization dedicated to bringing awarness to the institutional poverty issues in Syracuse, New York. We are actively working to encourage citizens of our city to give back to those who are in dire need of basic resources, such as food, water and shelter. Through this site, we will educate the public on how we can come together as a community to help others. </p>
</div>

