 <img src="myphoto.jpg" alt="Photo of Danielle Nimako" style="width:300px;height:350px;">
Danielle is a local Syracuse University Student who has decided to dedicate her remaining years to helping decrease the poverty rate in Syracuse. She is doing that by educating the youth by introducing them to STEM related fields, as well is utilzing resources on her university to give them basic life essentials. 

